headline: 3 Reasons EME Should Be High on Your Watchlist
summary: EMCOR currently trades at $454.41 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 424% since January 2020, blowing past the S&P 500’s 81.9% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 22.5% thanks to its solid quarterly results.
